{"tid":1631880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登大量分化撚 五毛進場","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:55.000Z","uid":228784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f13b42562c91746d0e699edf301c9ba1a89c801","tid":1631880,"uid":228784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"大家係咪唔記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做。不分化，不割蓆？</span></span><br />\n希望大家認清 連登從來都唔係大台<br />\n只係一個提供資訊既討論區<br />\n希望大家可以focus返行動同資訊post<br />\n唔好再比人帶到風向<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b998c00d517dad26cacb4fb24b319e2b736e64c","tid":1631880,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:19.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布！聽日係全民文宣日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631729</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1204b2110d4ef5d59259605ea419d5df6de44abb","tid":1631880,"uid":228784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:55.000Z","msg":"請大力推"},{"pid":"cd6d41ee7266235e07e23dcb19773ff92878bbb0","tid":1631880,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:16.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"aca43f6085586ac37f0e79cb87ab912701d2df8d","tid":1631880,"uid":228784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"Focus返行動post"},{"pid":"85da2de311aabf875afcf9bc705dfa8f9628f65c","tid":1631880,"uid":221919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"勿標籤 支持理性討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[求睇吓］請唔好孤立勇武 唔好重蹈覆轍！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628049</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6701f01899503e163361ae513eada67a2528b806","tid":1631880,"uid":228784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"推推"}]}